Feeling so thankful right now…

To begin, I just want to thank you guys for everything. I wouldn’t be standing here without you. I’m beyond grateful for each of you. I love you so so much.🥺

A big thank you to my @lorealparis family for this magical opportunity here at @festivaldecannes ♥️

Thank you to the amazing @givenchyofficial team for these incredible matching outfits, feeling so honored ♥️
